# Exclude build output and NuGet restore caches from the Docker build context.
# These Windows-generated files contain absolute paths (e.g. C:\Program Files\...)
# that break the Linux container build with MSB4018 / fallback package folder errors.

# .NET build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Test projects — not needed in production images
tests/

# IDE and OS artifacts
.vs/
.git/
.github/
.kiro/
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Infra files not needed in the image
infra/cloudformation/
infra/scripts/

# Markdown and docs
*.md
